ActAn Act to implement conventions between Canada and Morocco, Canada and Pakistan, Canada and Singapore, Canada and the Philippines, Canada and the Dominican Republic and Canada and Switzerland for the avoidance of double taxation with respect to income tax
SubjectSupplementary Convention for the Avoidance of Double Taxation and the Prevention of Fiscal Evasion With Respect to Taxes on Income - Singapore
PrecisOrder declaring that the supplementary convention, which was signed on November 29, 2011 and is intended to alter the Convention between Canada and the REPUBLIC OF SINGAPORE for the Avoidance of Double Taxation and the Prevention of Fiscal Evasion With Respect to Taxes on Income, done in Singapore on March 6, 1976, is approved by Canada.
